  "text": "3) Parameters Setup: We vary the number of seed nodes from 1% to 5%, and by default consider all nodes in the networks as targets. Sensitivity analysis experiments by varying the number of seeds and targets are given in [CITATION_1] . We also conduct experiments for both short-term and long-term with 30 and 500 time steps, respectively.",
